{"tid":1587154,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好亂搞九龍塘 完全出師無名","createTime":"2019-09-22T09:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T23:20:41.000Z","uid":36134,"like":18,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"776d9221e637b5e6e7af9b5329dd7cf909f174fd","tid":1587154,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"今次班有錢佬唔出聲幫港共已經係一種表態<br />\n唔好比仇富情緒蒙蔽到自己<br />\n你以為主動去九龍塘<br />\n令班有錢佬食tg<br />\n可以connect到佢地<br />\n點解會咁天真 定係諗野開始唔理性<br />\n主動同被動既分別要分清楚<br />\n今次你地主動引黑警過去放tg<br />\n分分鐘班狗開心到黎唔切<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時極可能就係黑警connect到班有錢佬<br />\n除時獲取更多社會資源打壓抗爭運動<br />\n仲有好多外國人<br />\n分分鐘影響埋國際戰線"},{"pid":"e5b95875db6c0e06f042c3089bdbcda922bb7055","tid":1587154,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed2253cc75f47f93eecb0cc0f1f51b9108f5b2ec","tid":1587154,"uid":160348,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:44:42.000Z","msg":"如果和平示威完俾黑警趕到去九龍塘就唔同講法，對否？"},{"pid":"1697eb2ae593dc683fc8652d0ad8de13c479fa64","tid":1587154,"uid":282490,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"咁就割嘅都唔會係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a885b434ab139a8efb70703f74e16aa21d1e1172","tid":1587154,"uid":158889,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:45:23.000Z","msg":"唔好再乜都唔好 而家叫你去打有錢佬？？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac91ba020ffb452f88789eb2994d76b3003f5d17","tid":1587154,"uid":224829,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c38b960f6e705756aa66ca5ebb0078fb6b002eb5","tid":1587154,"uid":36134,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed2253cc75f47f93eecb0cc0f1f51b9108f5b2ec